questions.quote: Phoebs, let me ask you something, were, were these, uh, funny brownies?
Oh! It will be fun! Ohh! Yay! Oh! Okay, ooh, let's plan the wedding reception. Wow! You really wanted me to do something with this van. Y'know what, I want you to take the chef job.
I know! I guess I am! Oh my god! Load up the Volvo I want to be a soccer mom!
